name: Frida Punk 015 - Send Nudes
description: Fun fact: Although Frida was popular in her lifetime, she was often dismissed as just being Diego Riveras wife. Her fame soared after her passing in 1954 and in the 1970's the art world experienced "Fridamania" and her work was in heavy demand. One of her most significant sales however was her piece "Two Nudes in a Forest" that sold in 2016 for $8 Million.
